305
00:21:41,619 --> 00:21:43,450
You learn well, Grasshopper.

306
00:21:47,299 --> 00:21:48,778
Task force, Campbell.

307
00:21:53,739 --> 00:21:54,854
All right.

308
00:21:58,219 --> 00:21:59,538
Two more bodies.

309
00:22:24,059 --> 00:22:25,094
Hey, slow down.

310
00:22:25,179 --> 00:22:27,613
It's all right, man, we'll be back later.

311
00:22:40,139 --> 00:22:42,699
Hey, man, get this virgin
