315
00:23:14,459 --> 00:23:16,415
Roden, squash that, man.

316
00:23:17,659 --> 00:23:19,331
Are you all right, Jack?

317
00:23:36,539 --> 00:23:38,370
-Jim, you got a minute?
-Sure.

318
00:23:38,459 --> 00:23:41,337
Careful, he wants to borrow money.
