329
00:24:26,379 --> 00:24:29,132
...get their cars repaired,
pictures developed...

330
00:24:29,219 --> 00:24:31,016
...anything, no matter how small.

331
00:24:31,099 --> 00:24:34,455
Do me a favor and get me copies
of these blood paintings on the walls...

332
00:24:34,539 --> 00:24:36,257
...in this stack of crime-scene photos.

333
00:24:36,339 --> 00:24:39,411
