and prison throughout the US.

334
00:24:39,499 --> 00:24:41,137
Maybe a former patient.

335
00:24:41,459 --> 00:24:43,529
I don't know, I just think that...

336
00:24:43,699 --> 00:24:47,009
...this work is so unique that any prisoner,
psychiatrist or priest...

337
00:24:47,099 --> 00:24:48,578
...would definitely not forget it.

338
00:24:48,659 --> 00:24:50,615
All right, everybody knows what to do.

339
00:24:50,699 --> 00:24:51,734
Let's go.

340
00:25:08,979 --> 00:25:10,332
No, I understand.

341
00:25:11,779 --> 00:25:13,770
I'll get there as fast as I can.

342
00:25:15,819 --> 00:25:16,774
Thanks.

343
00:25:16,859 --> 00:25:18,497
Hey, you're home early.

344
00:25:19,979 --> 00:25:21,048
