347
00:25:31,819 --> 00:25:33,696
There's been another killing.

348
00:25:35,499 --> 00:25:36,614
Same guy?

349
00:25:38,579 --> 00:25:39,455
Yeah.

350
00:25:39,579 --> 00:25:40,898
I'm sorry, Jack.

351
00:25:43,139 --> 00:25:45,130
He killed Ellen and her husband.

352
00:25:45,299 --> 00:25:46,448
