353
00:25:48,099 --> 00:25:51,296
I gotta go tell my kids
that their mother is dead.

354
00:25:53,139 --> 00:25:54,538
Jesus, Jack!

355
00:25:56,339 --> 00:25:58,807
I think he's makin' it personal, you know?

356
00:26:35,579 --> 00:26:37,171
Westlake Security.

