00:27:10,579 --> 00:27:11,489
Really?

363
00:27:12,259 --> 00:27:14,215
I wonder what took him so long?

364
00:27:14,459 --> 00:27:16,336
What would you like me to do?

365
00:27:18,099 --> 00:27:19,452
Ignore him.

