377
00:28:16,899 --> 00:28:18,730
Two coffees, Raffi. Extra sugar.

378
00:28:18,819 --> 00:28:21,128
-No coffee for me.
-They're both for me.

379
00:28:21,699 --> 00:28:22,893
Anything else?

380
00:28:23,619 --> 00:28:25,610
Nothin' in the military records.

381
00:28:26,099 --> 00:28:29,535
Almost nothin' before the NYPD.
Looks like this guy came out of nowhere.

382
00:28:29,619 --> 00:28:32,338
Are you tellin' me we don't know nothin'
about this guy?

383
00:28:32,419 --> 00:28:34,728
Yeah, there's one thing we know for sure.

384
00:28:34,819 --> 00:28:37,333
He used to be married
to the Dunleavy woman.

385
00:28:39,099 --> 00:28:40,327
Son of a bitch.

386
00:28:41,459 --> 00:28:45,418
"ln my Father's house,
there are many rooms. If it were not so...

387
00:28:45,819 --> 00:28:49,448
