401
00:29:39,299 --> 00:29:41,449
It's everything we know about you.

402
00:29:41,539 --> 00:29:43,769
Your background's nothin' but smoke
and mirrors.

403
00:29:43,859 --> 00:29:44,735
Who are you, Jack?

404
00:29:44,819 --> 00:29:46,093
I can't get into it right now.

405
00:29:46,179 --> 00:29:47,897
Yeah, well maybe you can get into this.

406
00:29:47,979 --> 00:29:50,493
We found your print
at your ex-wife's house.

407
00:29:52,299 --> 00:29:55,097
She was my ex-wife.
I pick up my kids there all the time.

408
00:29:55,179 --> 00:29:56,817
The print's on the body.

409
00:29:58,299 --> 00:29:59,448
Planted.

410
00:29:59,619 --> 00:30:02,008
And there's a puff of smoke
comin' from the grassy knoll.

411
00:30:02,099 --> 00:30:04,659
What kind of bullshit
you tryin' to run, man?

412
00:30:05,619 --> 00:30:09,055
I ain't always been a cop.
