413
00:30:10,659 --> 00:30:13,173
You are one mysterious motherfucker.

414
00:30:14,419 --> 00:30:16,614
Nobody seems to know anything
about your past...

415
00:30:16,699 --> 00:30:19,577
...and the only evidence I got
points right at you.

416
00:30:19,659 --> 00:30:21,934
Now, does that worry you, Jack?

417
00:30:23,219 --> 00:30:24,618
