445
00:32:37,699 --> 00:32:40,691
Yes, I do. Truly wicked. Sorry about Ellen.

446
00:32:42,779 --> 00:32:44,098
Wonderful woman.

447
00:32:45,699 --> 00:32:48,896
You know, the last two murders
were definitely the work of a pro...

448
00:32:48,979 --> 00:32:50,810
