449
00:32:50,979 --> 00:32:54,449
And I just have the feeling
that you might know who this pro is.

450
00:32:55,419 --> 00:32:57,137
Well, let me guess.

451
00:32:58,379 --> 00:33:00,176
They've discovered your checkered past...

452
00:33:00,259 --> 00:33:02,409
...and now they suspect you.

453
00:33:03,059 --> 00:33:04,412
Not exactly.

454
00:33:04,579 --> 00:33:08,538
They're still not totally up on my past yet,
but I know you are.

455
00:33:09,859 --> 00:33:13,010
Therefore, I'm sure you realize
what I'm capable of doing to you...

456
00:33:13,099 --> 00:33:14,498
...if I have to.

457
00:33:16,099 --> 00:33:17,771
Yes, indeed, I do.

458
00:33:17,859 --> 00:33:19,895
What kind of consultant you lookin' for?

459
00:33:19,979 --> 00:33:23,608
This individual gives me the impression
that he's a freelancer.

460
00:33:23,899 --> 00:33:26,777
Hiding his targets in the scenario
of a serial killer.

461
00:33:26,859 --> 00:33:29,054
Likes a .22, likes head shots.

462
00:33:29,779 --> 00:33:33,249
