467
00:33:44,859 --> 00:33:46,531
...testifying before Congress.

468
00:33:46,619 --> 00:33:50,771
They're getting kind of cranky
about where we get our core-op funds...

469
00:33:51,259 --> 00:33:53,011
...but, as it's you...

470
00:33:54,459 --> 00:33:56,609
