No, I said, "Best shot."

1024
01:22:12,539 --> 01:22:13,449
Boring.

1025
01:22:24,819 --> 01:22:26,730
Is that the best you got, boy?

1026
01:22:28,899 --> 01:22:32,209
If that's the best you got,
I'm just gonna have to kill you.

1027
01:22:35,819 --> 01:22:37,298
Is that all you got?

1028
01:22:55,299 --> 01:22:58,371
You don't look like you're gonna be
wakin' up happy now.

1029
01:23:38,019 --> 01:23:39,054
Hey, Capt.

1030
01:23:39,299 --> 01:23:41,130
You're looking a little rough there,
Campbell.

1031
01:23:41,219 --> 01:23:43,528
Yeah, well, they say I'm gonna make it.

1032
01:23:44,099 --> 01:23:45,771
Guess I owe you an apology, Jack.

1033
01:23:45,859 --> 01:23:47,577
God, wouldn't that be nice?

1034
01:23:48,419 --> 01:23:50,330
Well, you're not gonna get it.

1035
01:23:51,499 --> 01:23:53,217
But I do owe it to you.

1036
01:23:54,339 --> 01:23:56,614
Do me a favor,
tell my wife I'm alive and well.

1037
01:23:56,699 --> 01:23:58,018
You got it.

1038
01:23:58,259 --> 01:23:59,214
Feel better, kid.

1039
01:23:59,299 --> 01:24:00,175
Yeah.

1040
01:24:02,339 --> 01:24:05,809
Say, Jack. How about we not talk
for a couple of days?

1041
01:24:06,699 --> 01:24:08,052
Somethin' I said?

1042
01:24:08,179 --> 01:24:11,455
It's just that ever since
you started bein' my partner...

1043
01:24:12,059 --> 01:24:14,448
...l've been beat up, blown up...

1044
01:24:15,819 --> 01:24:17,855
...shot, kicked out a window...

1045
01:24:18,939 --> 01:24:21,772
...all my worldly possessions
burnt to a crisp.

1046
01:24:22,219 --> 01:24:24,096
Basically, I'm homeless.

1047
01:24:25,179 --> 01:24:27,329
Not one good thing has happened
since I met you.

1048
01:24:27,419 --> 01:24:28,932
You got to try powdered deer penis.

1049
01:24:29,019 --> 01:24:30,372
