1050
01:24:30,459 --> 01:24:33,292
Don't call me, Jack.
Don't leave me a message.

1051
01:24:33,459 --> 01:24:37,372
Don't fax me. If I see a bird on my window
with a message on its foot...

1052
01:24:37,539 --> 01:24:39,370
...l'm throwin' him back out.

1053
01:24:39,459 --> 01:24:40,209
Don't send flowers.

1054
